A man sits on the notorious koppie in Marikana on the seventh anniversary of the massacre. eNCA's Xoli Mngambi speaks to a miner on the infamous Koppie in Marikana about the day that saw miners and police clashing seven years ago. Amcu members and residents sit on the Marikana koppie ahead of the commemoration ceremony. Some residents set up food stalls, ahead of the Marikana Massacre commemorations on 16 August 2019. Police monitored the crowds at the koppie in Marikana on the seventh anniversary of the massacre. Amcu members gather in Marikana on 16 August 2019 Amcu members demonstrate in Marikana on 16 August 2019 Women make their way to the Marikana Massacre memorial on 16 August 2019 A Marikana resident arrives at the commemorations on 16 August 2019 with his mule.